data.description: Nestled within the serene community of Saint Cloud, this charming property, offers a blend of modern convenience and traditional allure.  Approaching the residence, a well-manicured front yard with lush greenery welcomes you, hinting at the care and attention given to the home. The architecture boasts a timeless design, featuring a warm painted exterior and a welcoming porch, perfect for enjoying quiet moments or greeting guests. Upon entering, you're greeted by a spacious and inviting interior. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living room, dining area, and kitchen, creating an ideal space for both relaxation and entertainment. Large windows allow natural light to illuminate the rooms, enhancing the inviting ambiance. The kitchen, adorned with modern appliances and ample counter space, is a haven for culinary enthusiasts, offering the perfect setup for creating delightful meals. The house comprises four bedrooms, each exuding comfort and tranquility. The master suite, with its en-suite bathroom, provides a private sanctuary to unwind after a long day. Stepping outside, the backyard presents a private retreat. A well-maintained garden area provides a peaceful setting for outdoor gatherings, barbecues, or simply enjoying the fresh air. Conveniently located near shopping, schools, and parks, with a perfect blend of a quiet neighborhood setting and accessibility to the vibrant Saint Cloud community. This property embodies the essence of a welcoming home, inviting you to create cherished memories in a space that balances comfort, style, and a sense of community.
